entries.journal_entry_description: A Nova Orion freighter broke down and needs parts for repair. Go pick up those parts and deliver them to the freighter. Then escort the freighter across Corellia space
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Deliver parts needed for repairs to a Nova Orion freighter that broke down and then escort them as they make their delivery.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Dexen Eronoss on Nova Orion Station.
